org.apache.hadoop.hive.common.io.encoded

Class EncodedColumnBatch<BatchKey>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.common.io.encoded.EncodedColumnBatch<BatchKey>

  • public class EncodedColumnBatch<BatchKey>
extends Object
    A block of data for a given section of a file, similar to VRB but in encoded form. Stores a set of buffers for each encoded stream that is a part of each column.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  EncodedColumnBatch.ColumnStreamData
      Slice of the data for a stream for some column, stored inside MemoryBuffer's.
